  <thing-type id="merten_507502_00_000" listed="false">
    <label>507502 Flush-mounted switch</label>
    <description><![CDATA[
Flush-mounted switch<br /><h1>Overview</h1><p>The flush-mounted receiver can be used to switch loads on and off via radio (for information about permitted loads, see the technical data). When it receives the radio signal, the flush-mounted receiver switches the corresponding contact.</p> <br /><h2>Inclusion Information</h2><p>Triple click on the switch button</p> <br /><h2>Exclusion Information</h2><p>Triple click on the switch button</p> <br /><h2>Wakeup Information</h2><p>Triple click on the switch button</p>
    ]]></description>
    <category>WallSwitch</category>

    <!-- CHANNEL DEFINITIONS -->
